content:
Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, and more.

Get Started Using CRM Analytics by setting up the platform, integrating data into datasets, and exploring data directly at source. Build dashboards, embed and customize analytics, and create apps to give business users a deeper understanding of their data.

Develop with CRM Analytics using Intelligent Analytics Apps like Tableau and Unified Analytics Experiences. Use Einstein Discovery for advanced analytics capabilities.

Track auto-installed app usage by viewing charts on the main page or individual app pages, which show API calls per hour and dataset rows used per day. The API statistics are updated hourly, while dataset row statistics are updated at midnight UTC.
title: Tracking Auto-Installed App Usage in Salesforce Analytics
